high_descs: Turn around, move to the computer on the coffee table.
Pick up the computer on the coffee table.
Bring the computer to the ottoman on the other side of the coffee table.
Put the computer down on the ottoman, left of the phone.
anns.task_desc: Put a computer on the ottoman.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the end of the coffee table, behind you.
Shut the laptop closed and pick it up from the coffee table.
Go to the ottoman in front of you, on the other side of the coffee table.
Place the laptop on the ottoman, to the left of the cell phone.
anns.task_desc: Put the laptop on the ottoman.

high_descs: Turn right and take one step then turn right and walk to the table.
Close the laptop and then pick up the laptop from the table.
Turn right and take one step then turn left and walk to the purple chair.
Put the laptop down to the left of the red cell phone on the purple chair.
anns.task_desc: Move the laptop to the chair.
